data.description: New Price for this Oasis in Vista! This Gorgeous Estate is an Entertainers Delight! Luscious Landscaping welcomes you with curved entrance! It Features 3 Bedrooms 2 Bathrooms PLUS/1 Oversized Bedroom downstairs with separate sliding glass doors for guests, teenagers or another family room- you choose! Kitchen is lovely with light counters, tons of cabinets and an island for serving and dining. Home boasts natural light in every room! Step into the backyard through the sliding glass doors off the kitchen onto an elevated deck with built in seating for guests! Cool off in the Sparkling Pool, while enjoying the Custom Built Bar including the BBQ Grills. There's also a Sauna, Storage Shed and so much more room to play!! Walk the curvy sidewalk to an area where you can possibly build an ADU up to 1000 sqft! A New Fence has been built for privacy! Long DriveWay for toys, RV Parking and parking for your ADU residents! Home also has Solar! No HOA & No Fees!
